Vue Azure Maps

Integrate Azure Maps in your Vue application

Get Started →

Simple

Integrate clear, easy-to-read maps in your Vue application with ease.

Powerful

It supports markers, controls, points, lines, polygons, layers, user position, and more.

Component-oriented

You can declaratively render map components to the DOM using straightforward template syntax.
